---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AIGIS | Levenhall" description="AIGIS is Levenhall's AI evaluation and governance platform for the private sector — the substrate for AI insurability, regulatory compliance, and continuous risk assessment.">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="a-hero">
        <div class="a-hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="a-hero-grid"></div>
        <div class="a-hero-inner">
            <p class="a-tag">A Levenhall Product</p>
            <h1 class="a-wordmark">AIGIS</h1>
            <p class="a-tagline">AI evaluation &amp; governance for the enterprise &mdash; the substrate for AI insurability.</p>
            <div class="a-cta">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request Early Access</a>
                <a href="#how" class="btn btn-outline-white">How It Works</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── THE INSURANCE PROBLEM ── -->
    <section class="a-section a-problem">
        <div class="a-narrow reveal">
            <p class="a-lede"><span class="a-drop">A</span>I is now deployed inside every regulated industry. Underwriters, risk committees, and compliance officers have no standardized way to determine whether a deployment is insurable, defensible, or compliant &mdash; and the deployments don't stop while they figure it out.</p>
            <p>AIGIS exists to answer one question, continuously: <em>is this model safe and mission-ready for this user, on this network, doing this job, under this regulatory regime?</em></p>
            <p>It is the operational evaluator's infrastructure. Not a research bench. Not a one-time audit. A continuous assessment substrate that AI insurance, regulatory compliance, and enterprise risk all run on top of.</p>
            <p class="a-problem-close">Insurance is the headline use case. Governance, regulatory reporting, and enterprise risk management ride the same rails.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── INSURANCE TRACK ── -->
    <section class="a-section a-insurance">
        <div class="a-insurance-bg"></div>
        <div class="a-narrow reveal" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
            <span class="a-eyebrow a-eyebrow-light">§ The insurance track</span>
            <h2>An insurable AI deployment is one that can be continuously evaluated.</h2>
            <p>Insurers cannot price what they cannot measure. AIGIS produces the continuous evaluation record that turns an AI deployment into a measurable risk: every run captured with a full environment snapshot, every prompt-injection or jailbreak probe logged against MITRE ATLAS, every degradation event reproducible, every model and prompt versioned.</p>
            <p>For underwriters: a continuous signal to price against. For brokers: a defensible record at renewal. For the enterprise: the compliance evidence the insurer needs without a fire drill every quarter.</p>

            <div class="a-insurance-pills reveal">
                <span class="a-pill"><strong>$60M+</strong> &nbsp;in tracked AI insurance coverage on the platform</span>
                <span class="a-pill"><strong>6</strong> &nbsp;regulatory frameworks mapped to evaluation outputs</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── THREE TRACKS ── -->
    <section class="a-section a-tracks" id="how">
        <div class="a-narrow reveal">
            <span class="a-eyebrow">§ What's inside</span>
            <h2>Three tracks on one harness.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="a-tracks-grid reveal">
            <article class="a-track">
                <span class="a-track-num">I.</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Evaluation</h3>
                    <p>One uniform protocol behind adapters for OpenAI, HuggingFace, Bedrock, gRPC, and local Ollama. Pluggable scorers covering exact match, similarity, classification, and routed human evaluation &mdash; with Krippendorff's alpha and Fleiss' kappa for inter-rater reliability. Every run captures a full environment snapshot so a result is reproducible months later.</p>
                    <p>Domains: general, safety, adversarial, agentic, multimodal, and customer-specific benchmarks built on Levenhall's eight-phase methodology.</p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="a-track">
                <span class="a-track-num">II.</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Adversarial &amp; Operational Stress</h3>
                    <p>An automated red-teaming pipeline aligned to MITRE ATLAS &mdash; prompt injection, jailbreak generation, data-poisoning probes, model-extraction resistance &mdash; with results mapped to ATLAS technique IDs that an insurer or auditor recognizes.</p>
                    <p>An operational-stress simulator injects latency, jitter, throttling, and intermittent connectivity, then measures degradation curves rather than binary pass/fail. Agentic evaluation captures full execution traces and scores against OWASP Agentic AI Top 10 and the MAESTRO framework.</p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="a-track">
                <span class="a-track-num">III.</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Governance, Risk &amp; Insurance</h3>
                    <p>Live coverage against the frameworks insurers and regulators actually use: <strong>NIST AI RMF</strong>, <strong>ISO 42001</strong>, the <strong>EU AI Act</strong>, <strong>MITRE ATLAS</strong>, <strong>OWASP Agentic AI Top 10</strong>, and the <strong>DoD AI Ethical Principles</strong>. Risk scoring against active incidents. Insurance coverage monitoring across the portfolio. An activity feed that surfaces new evaluations, adversarial detections, and bias audits in real time.</p>
                    <p>The output is a defensible governance trail, refreshed continuously, not a snapshot taken once a year.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── DEPLOYMENT FLEXIBILITY ── -->
    <section class="a-section a-deploy" id="deploy">
        <div class="a-narrow reveal">
            <span class="a-eyebrow">§ Deployment</span>
            <h2>Same container. Every environment.</h2>
            <p class="a-deploy-lede">Vendor-agnostic. Identical container images for managed cloud, segregated networks, and air-gapped environments &mdash; the only thing that changes is a Helm config.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="a-deploy-tabs reveal">
            <div class="a-tab a-tab-active">
                <span class="a-tab-label">cloud.yaml</span>
                <pre class="a-code"><span class="a-c-key">llm</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">provider</span>: <span class="a-c-val">openai</span>
  <span class="a-c-key">model</span>: <span class="a-c-val">gpt-4o</span>
<span class="a-c-key">vector</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">backend</span>: <span class="a-c-val">managed-cloud</span>
<span class="a-c-key">network</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">egress</span>: <span class="a-c-val">full</span></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="a-tab">
                <span class="a-tab-label">segregated.yaml</span>
                <pre class="a-code"><span class="a-c-key">llm</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">provider</span>: <span class="a-c-val">azure-openai</span>
  <span class="a-c-key">model</span>: <span class="a-c-val">gpt-4o</span>
<span class="a-c-key">vector</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">backend</span>: <span class="a-c-val">pgvector</span>
<span class="a-c-key">network</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">egress</span>: <span class="a-c-val">restricted</span></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="a-tab">
                <span class="a-tab-label">airgapped.yaml</span>
                <pre class="a-code"><span class="a-c-key">llm</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">provider</span>: <span class="a-c-val">ollama</span>
  <span class="a-c-key">model</span>: <span class="a-c-val">llama3-70b-q4</span>
<span class="a-c-key">vector</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">backend</span>: <span class="a-c-val">pgvector</span>
<span class="a-c-key">network</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">egress</span>: <span class="a-c-val">none</span></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="a-deploy-footer reveal">
            <p>Open-source underneath. No vendor lock-in at the layer that matters. For institutions running sensitive deployments &mdash; financial services, healthcare, regulated dual-use technology, defense primes, intelligence community &mdash; the same image runs air-gapped against a local Ollama model.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── WHO IT'S FOR ── -->
    <section class="a-section a-audience">
        <div class="a-narrow reveal">
            <span class="a-eyebrow">§ Who it's for</span>
            <h2>Built for the private sector first.</h2>
            <p>AI insurance underwriters and brokers writing or pricing coverage for enterprise AI risk. Compliance and risk committees inside regulated enterprises &mdash; financial services, healthcare, energy, critical infrastructure, dual-use technology &mdash; that need a defensible governance trail. Enterprise AI leads who have to answer to insurers, auditors, and boards on the same model.</p>
            <p class="a-audience-foot">Defense and intelligence community engagements run on the same platform, in air-gapped mode. The product is dual-use; the lead is the private sector.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ── -->
    <section class="a-cta-section">
        <div class="a-cta-bg"></div>
        <div class="a-cta-inner">
            <div class="a-cta-rule"></div>
            <p class="a-cta-eyebrow">Levenhall Proprietary</p>
            <h2>AIGIS is active. Early access is selective.</h2>
            <p>We work with AI insurance counterparties, regulated enterprises, and institutional risk teams on early access. The platform architecture, adapter SDK, governance-integrated scoring, operational-stress profiling, and benchmark methodology are Levenhall proprietary.</p>
            <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request Early Access</a>
                <a href="/services#market-intelligence" class="btn btn-outline-white">Intelligence Practice</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* ── HERO ── */
    .a-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(160deg, #04070e 0%, #080e1c 30%, #0f1f3a 70%, #0c1628 100%);
        padding: 9rem 2rem 5rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .a-hero-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .a-hero-grid {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 60px 60px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
        -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
    }

    .a-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.5), transparent);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .a-hero-inner {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .a-tag {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.66rem;
        letter-spacing: 3.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .a-wordmark {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 6.5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 16px;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1;
        margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
        text-indent: 16px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 40%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.5) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .a-tagline {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        letter-spacing: -0.2px;
    }

    .a-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* ── SHARED ── */
    .a-section { padding: 6rem 0; }

    .a-narrow {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .a-eyebrow {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 2.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }

    .a-eyebrow-light { color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85); }

    /* ── PROBLEM ── */
    .a-problem { background: var(--cream); }

    .a-lede {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.7rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
    }

    .a-drop {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--gold);
        line-height: 0.85;
        float: left;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem 0 0;
    }

    .a-problem p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .a-problem em {
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--burgundy);
    }

    .a-problem-close {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.2rem !important;
        color: var(--burgundy) !important;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        padding-top: 1.4rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    /* ── INSURANCE TRACK ── */
    .a-insurance {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a1628 0%, var(--deep-navy) 100%);
        padding: 6rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .a-insurance-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 30%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 70%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .a-insurance::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.3);
    }

    .a-insurance h2 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.2vw, 2.5rem);
        line-height: 1.18;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.6px;
    }

    .a-insurance p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .a-insurance-pills {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.7rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .a-pill {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.2);
        padding: 0.55rem 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .a-pill strong {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.95);
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }

    /* ── TRACKS ── */
    .a-tracks { background: var(--cream); }

    .a-tracks .a-narrow {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .a-tracks h2 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        letter-spacing: -0.6px;
    }

    .a-tracks-grid {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 2rem auto 0;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .a-track {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        padding: 2.4rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.12);
    }

    .a-track:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .a-track-num {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        color: var(--gold);
        line-height: 1;
        text-align: right;
        padding-top: 0.4rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .a-track h3 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }

    .a-track p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }

    .a-track p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .a-track strong {
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── DEPLOYMENT ── */
    .a-deploy {
        background: var(--stone);
        padding: 6rem 0 6.5rem;
    }

    .a-deploy h2 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.6px;
    }

    .a-deploy-lede {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--burgundy);
        line-height: 1.55;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .a-deploy-tabs {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 3rem auto 2.5rem;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .a-tab {
        background: #0a1628;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .a-tab-active {
        border-color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.4);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.15);
    }

    .a-tab:hover {
        border-color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.3);
    }

    .a-tab-label {
        display: block;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', 'Consolas', monospace;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85);
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .a-code {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 1.2rem 1.2rem;
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', 'Consolas', monospace;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
        white-space: pre;
        overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .a-c-key { color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85); }
    .a-c-val { color: var(--gold); }

    .a-deploy-footer {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .a-deploy-footer p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
    }

    /* ── AUDIENCE ── */
    .a-audience { background: var(--cream); padding: 5rem 0; }

    .a-audience h2 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
        line-height: 1.2;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .a-audience p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .a-audience-foot {
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--text-medium) !important;
        font-size: 0.98rem !important;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        padding-top: 1.2rem;
        margin-top: 0.6rem;
    }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .a-cta-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #060b16 0%, var(--deep-navy) 50%, #162d4f 100%);
        padding: 5.5rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .a-cta-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 0%, transparent 40%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .a-cta-section::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.5), transparent);
    }

    .a-cta-inner {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .a-cta-rule {
        width: 30px;
        height: 1px;
        background: var(--gold);
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    }

    .a-cta-eyebrow {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85);
        margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }

    .a-cta-section h2 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.2vw, 2.6rem);
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.15;
        letter-spacing: -0.6px;
    }

    .a-cta-section p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        font-size: 1.02rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .a-hero { padding: 7rem 2rem 4rem; }
        .a-section { padding: 4.5rem 0; }
        .a-deploy { padding: 4.5rem 0; }
        .a-insurance { padding: 4.5rem 0; }
        .a-deploy-tabs { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.8rem; }
        .a-code { font-size: 0.78rem; }
        .a-lede { font-size: 1.35rem; }
        .a-drop { font-size: 2.6rem; }
        .a-track { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 2rem 0; }
        .a-track-num { text-align: left; font-size: 2rem; padding-top: 0; }
        .a-insurance-pills { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    }
</style>
